{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8340eab1-881e-4788-86b7-9a903b365198", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8340eab1-881e-4788-86b7-9a903b365198@1.pkg/1772597545206/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597545383", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8340eab1-881e-4788-86b7-9a903b365198@1.pkg/1772597545206/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597545383"}, "identifier": "8340eab1-881e-4788-86b7-9a903b365198", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>题考查依法行使权利，自觉履行义务、违反义务须承担责任。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C:杨某在某短视频平台发布&ldquo;山西大同发生了9.6级地震&rdquo;的谣言，被公安机关依法行政拘留，警示我们要依法正确行使权利，自觉履行义务，不做违反道德和法律的事，故C符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A:网络不是法外之地，自由是有约束的，不违法是人们行为的底线，而非道德，故A说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：行政违法行为要承担行政责任，犯罪要承担刑事责任，民事违法行为要承担民事责任，从&ldquo;行政拘留10日&rdquo;可知承担行政责任。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：题干没有体现法律由国家制定，故C不符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>4.1中国的机遇与挑战</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年1月，杨某在某短视频平台发布&ldquo;山西大同发生了9.6级地震&rdquo;的谣言，引发民众恐慌。公安机关依法对杨某出行政拘留10日的处罚。该案例警示我们（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）2025年1月，杨某在某短视频平台发布“山西大同发生了9.6级地震”的谣言，引发民众恐慌。公安机关依法对杨某出行政拘留10日的处罚。该案例警示我们（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8340eab1-881e-4788-86b7-9a903b365198@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755140540385", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>网络空间自由无拘束，道德是行为底线</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>此行为有严重社会危害性，负刑事责任</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>网民应该依法行使权利，自觉履行义务</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>法律由国家制定、国家强制力保证实施</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年1月，杨某在某短视频平台发布&ldquo;山西大同发生了9.6级地震&rdquo;的谣言，引发民众恐慌。公安机关依法对杨某出行政拘留10日的处罚。该案例警示我们（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source"